in the middle, like you said,

259
00:16:57,481 --> 00:16:59,847
and we're putting
the shelf in the hall.

260
00:16:59,917 --> 00:17:02,147
Yes, but no more
than two days though.

261
00:17:02,220 --> 00:17:05,383
Sure, unless you want us
to give the bathroom a coat of paint.

262
00:17:05,456 --> 00:17:08,050
It wouldn't hurt.

263
00:17:08,125 --> 00:17:11,390
- I can't spend any more money.
- We'll meet you halfway...

264
00:17:11,462 --> 00:17:13,157
Since we're already at it.

265
00:17:13,231 --> 00:17:15,756
