309
00:20:36,033 --> 00:20:37,660
By the way,

310
00:20:37,735 --> 00:20:39,032
are you Mr. Oliveri?

311
00:20:39,103 --> 00:20:40,730
Yes.

312
00:20:40,805 --> 00:20:44,138
Mr. Terzetti was very pleased

313
00:20:44,208 --> 00:20:45,903
