you did at his house.

314
00:20:45,976 --> 00:20:48,171
I'm glad.

315
00:20:48,245 --> 00:20:50,770
Are you expensive?

316
00:20:50,848 --> 00:20:52,509
I wouldn't say so.

317
00:20:52,583 --> 00:20:55,108
I need to repaper my living room

318
00:20:55,186 --> 00:20:57,211
