but my budget's limited.

319
00:20:57,288 --> 00:20:58,550
How much will it cost?

320
00:20:58,622 --> 00:21:01,989
If you want,
I'll come and make an estimate.

321
00:21:02,059 --> 00:21:04,721
I live on the same floor
as Terzetti.

322
00:21:04,795 --> 00:21:07,059
Would you like anything else?

323
00:21:07,131 --> 00:21:10,066
I need some bread.

324
00:21:21,512 --> 00:21:23,036
Thank you.

325
00:21:32,256 --> 00:21:34,588
- May I come in?
- Yes.

326
00:21:36,927 --> 00:21:38,895
Here's the pizza and the beer.

327
00:21:38,963 --> 00:21:41,397
Thank you.
Please give it to me.

328
00:21:42,833 --> 00:21:45,700
Thank you.
