394
00:26:25,916 --> 00:26:28,749
- Seriously.
- It's better this way, better for you.

395
00:26:28,819 --> 00:26:30,844
No problem at all, Vito.

396
00:27:30,747 --> 00:27:32,271
So how is it going?

397
00:27:32,349 --> 00:27:35,182
- Fine.
- How nice!

398
00:27:35,252 --> 00:27:37,880
- Would you like a coffee?
- Why not?

399
00:27:37,955 --> 00:27:39,354
I'll have it ready soon.

400
00:27:39,423 --> 00:27:42,017
- Thanks, ma'am.
- You're welcome.

401
00:29:36,673 --> 00:29:39,733
What the fuck am I doing?

402
00:30:49,079 --> 00:30:50,569
Here they are!

403
00:30:50,647 --> 00:30:54,105
