all the way here.

404
00:30:54,184 --> 00:30:57,881
Next time you can make a transfer
with the bank, as usual.

405
00:30:59,856 --> 00:31:02,620
Okay. Goodbye.

406
00:31:06,063 --> 00:31:08,395
- How are you?
- It's Michele, Dad.

407
00:31:08,465 --> 00:31:12,094
