408
00:31:12,169 --> 00:31:14,194
So how are you?

409
00:31:14,271 --> 00:31:16,364
So-so.

410
00:31:16,440 --> 00:31:18,465
Some issues at work.

411
00:31:18,542 --> 00:31:20,635
