445
00:33:12,289 --> 00:33:14,382
Excuse me,
where is your husband?

446
00:33:14,457 --> 00:33:16,584
Here, this is
the advance you gave me,

447
00:33:16,660 --> 00:33:18,628
and this is for your trouble.

448
00:33:18,695 --> 00:33:19,957
